transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) r1 = 2 / length(p_in) r2 = 0.5 / length(p_in) a1 = fmod(p_in.x, p_in.y) a2 = fmod(p_in.y, p_in.x) a = sin(lerp(abs(a1), abs(a2), 0.5)) b1 = fmod(p_in.x * p_in.y, length(p_in)) b2 = fmod(length2(p_in), length(p_in)) b = sin(lerp(abs(b1), abs(b2), 0.5)) z = if r < twoinvpi() then fmod(b, a) else recip(fmod(b, a)) / pi() con0 = abs(z) > r1 con1 = abs(z) < r1 && abs(z) > r2 con2 = abs(z) < r2 in (if if fill <= 0.0 then con0 else if fill > 0.25 then con2 else con1 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
